The build failed because dart branch "release-6.1" no longer exists. I tried to build with branch "release-6.2" but it appears to still have tried 6.1:

* https://build.osrfoundation.org/view/upstream-dart/job/gazebo-any_dart4-devel-xenial-amd64-gpu-nvidia_docker/36/

~~~
# BEGIN SECTION: compiling DART from source
+ '[' -d /var/lib/jenkins/workspace/gazebo-any_dart4-devel-xenial-amd64-gpu-nvidia_docker/dart ']'
+ cd /var/lib/jenkins/workspace/gazebo-any_dart4-devel-xenial-amd64-gpu-nvidia_docker/dart
+ git pull
Your configuration specifies to merge with the ref 'refs/heads/release-6.1'
from the remote, but no such ref was fetched.
~~~
